.TH wxGenericDirCtrl 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxGenericDirCtrl \- This control can be used to place a directory listing (with optional files) on an arbitrary window.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The control contains a \fIwxTreeCtrl\fR window representing the directory hierarchy, and optionally, a \fIwxChoice\fR window containing a list of filters.

.SS "Styles"

.PP
This class supports the following styles:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
wxDIRCTRL_DIR_ONLY: Only show directories, and not files.

.RE


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
